sequenceDiagram
    participant User1 as User 1
    participant User2 as User 2
    participant Server as Server

    User1->>Server: Change online status to "Online"
    Server-->>User2: Notify User 1 is online
    User2->>Server: Change online status to "Online"
    Server-->>User1: Notify User 2 is online

    User1->>Server: Start typing
    Server-->>User2: Notify User 1 is typing
    User2->>Server: Set privacy controls (hide typing indicators)
    Server-->>User1: Notify User 2 has hidden typing indicators

    User1->>Server: Stop typing
    Server-->>User2: Notify User 1 has stopped typing